    "• Cassava: This crop thrives in warm, tropical climates and can tolerate poor soil conditions.",
    "With the projected increase in temperature, Cassava could be a viable option.",
    "• Yam: Another popular crop in Nigeria, it requires well-drained loamy soil which can be enhanced by proper soil management.",
